Package com.g1.mychess.match.dto

Class MatchResultDTO

java.lang.Object
com.g1.mychess.match.dto.MatchResultDTO
public class MatchResultDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for representing the result of a chess match. This class contains details about the match ID, winner ID, loser ID, and whether the match was a draw.
